  <brief_title>Pneumatic Retinopexy Versus Vitrectomy for Retinal Detachment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Trial Comparing Pneumatic Retinopexy Versus Vitrectomy for the Management of Primary Retinal Detachment; Anatomical Success, Functional Success and Impact on Patient Quality of Life</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
